  <TITLE>Widgets support for &quot;nop-card&quot;</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>The original suggested was posted at https://github.com/nopSolutions/nopCommerce/issues/6798. But in order to avoid logic duplication for all nop-cards, let's add a general way to add widgets before and after any &quot;card&quot; So we have to extend the &quot;NopCardTagHelper&quot; class to invoke two new widget zones (before and after the card). Let's pass a specified &quot;NAME_ATTRIBUTE_NAME&quot; as parameter to it, so it could be used to identify what card is rendered now.</DESCRIPTION>
